text: Conny Kissling (born 18 July 1961) is a Swiss freestyle skier, world champion and Olympic participant. She competed at the 1992 Winter Olympics in Albertville, in women's moguls. Her achievements at the FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships include one gold medal in combined in 1986, and three silver medals.
